original_title: AKB48グループリクエストアワー セットリストベスト100 2016
overview: The AKB48 Request Hour Setlist Best 100 2016 (AKB48 リクエストアワー セットリストベスト100 2016) was held from January 22 to January 24, 2016 at Tokyo Dome City Hall. Fans made their voices heard by voting for their favorite AKB48/SKE48/NMB48/HKT48/SDN48/JKT48/SNH48 original songs.
title: AKB48 Group Request Hour Setlist Best 100 2016
